description: SignalingRadioBearer: Table containing signaling radio bearer parameters for various cells at specific times.  Columns: dateTime (timestamp), Area_Name (cell area), CellId (cell identifier), Id2 (secondary cell identifier), Id3 (additional identifier), Id4 (additional identifier), vsDataType (data type), vsDataFormatVersion (data format version), SignalingRadioBearer.tReassemblyUl (UL reassembly timer), SignalingRadioBearer.tReassemblyDl (DL reassembly timer), SignalingRadioBearer.tPollRetransmitUl (UL poll retransmission timer), SignalingRadioBearer.dlMaxRetxThreshold (DL max retransmission threshold), SignalingRadioBearer.tPollRetransmitDl (DL poll retransmission timer), SignalingRadioBearer.ulMaxRetxThreshold (UL max retransmission threshold), SignalingRadioBearer.signalingRadioBearerId (signaling radio bearer ID), SignalingRadioBearer.tReorderingUl (UL reordering timer), SignalingRadioBearer.tReorderingDl (DL reordering timer), SignalingRadioBearer.tReorderingUlNb (UL reordering buffer size), SignalingRadioBearer.tPollRetransmitNbUl (UL poll retransmission buffer size), SignalingRadioBearer.tReorderingDlNb (DL reordering buffer size), SignalingRadioBearer.tPollRetransmitNbDl (DL poll retransmission buffer size).
